# Lock Files Configuration
# - uv.lock: Committed (ensures reproducible Python builds)
# - Cargo.lock: Ignore for libraries, commit for binaries (project-cli)
# - pnpm-lock.yaml: Ignore for library packages (consumers resolve their own deps)
pnpm-lock.yaml
**/Cargo.lock
!rust/project-cli/Cargo.lock

